      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in reliable running order. The exterior has sustained significant damage, including large dents, pervasive rust spots, and heavily oxidized paint. Inside, the upholstery is torn and the electronics are largely non-functional. This car is best suited as a project for a dedicated restorer or as a source for spare parts, as it will require extensive mechanical and cosmetic work to return to the road.",
