    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in unblemished condition, featuring a pristine exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Mechanically superior and rigorously inspected, this motorcar offers an uncompromising driving experience for the most discerning enthusiast. Rare in its level of upkeep, it represents a definitive acquisition for those who demand peak quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
